Strong candidates will discuss: CSS Grid with custom properties for dynamic sizing, transform-based animations to avoid layout thrashing, virtualization techniques for large widget counts, and fallback strategies for older browsers.

## Code Example
```css
.dashboard {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--cols, 12), 1fr);
  gap: var(--gap, 16px);
